description:
This is a 11 minute workout called 'Heat Building Flow' from the channel Owen Henn.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Yoga.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Groove Session and The Meditative Grind vibe.
The The Groove Session vibe means Fun, fluid, expressive, completely in the moment. This is especially good for Days when you want to move intuitively and just vibe. The The Meditative Grind vibe means Zone in, lock down, let repetition take over. This is especially good for Those who love a slow burn and rhythmic intensity..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Warm-up with Owen and Nick during this fast paced flow designed to build your body heat....
